Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: RB Medical Plaza is conveniently located in the heart of Towne Center Rancho Bernardo. The building has distinctive Spanish style architecture including a central courtyard appointed with a beautiful fountain featuring handcrafted statues and lush landscaping. RB Medical Plaza has a generous parking ratio and ownership has been careful to pay special attention to detail with amenities such as coffee sinks, operable windows, hardwood floors, and an executive conferencing facility that is available to all tenants free of charge. The building has men’s and women’s showers and lockers. The property is impeccably maintained and professionally managed.

Common.LocationDescription.Common.Text: This property is located in the City of Hawthorne on the entire square city block of bordered by W. 116th ST, W 118th St, Ramona Ave, and Grevillea Ave. It is also an entry point for over 60 million travelers who come through LAX, the sixth busiest airport in the world. Hawthorne is currently experiencing a transformation that will reshape the landscape of this critical Westside city.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
The Robert F. Kennedy Medical Center is a 274-bed hospital located on an 8-acre site in the heart of Hawthorne. Originally built in 1926, the 280,000 SF hospital has since undergone extensive renovations which includes the construction of a new 60,000 SF building built to current hospital requirements for the ER/ICU units. 

The site is located in a residentially dense neighborhood in close proximity to the Hawthorne Airport/SpaceX, the Forum, the new SoFi NFL stadium, LAX, and many national chain and local restaurants, with easy access to the 105 & 405 freeways.
